  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Sitaxsentan in the Treatment of Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Safety and Efficacy Study of Sitaxsentan Sodium Treatment in Patients With Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension</official_title>
